## Technical Description

This project provides a governance spine for multi-agent AI systems, featuring:
- Agent Amethyst meta-orchestration and QA authority
- Agent Apogee evidence governance and evaluation protocols
- Agent Sentinel integrity enforcement and safety boundaries
- MDAR (Monitor-Detect-Assess-Respond) loop specifications
- NIST AI Risk Management Framework alignment
- OWASP Agentic Top 10 safety sweep integration
- Phi-Harmonic Gating convergence patterns (1-1-1-1 Gate, Triad Consensus, Platinum Strata)
- Gold Star certification validation processes
- Enterprise-grade governance and compliance standards
- NDR Pattern Registry (P-01 through P-33+)

Designed for institutional and enterprise deployment of secure,
governance-aligned multi-agent AI systems.

